text: Clifford Kettemborough (born 8 June 1953) is an American author and business professional. == Career == Kettemborough’s formal educational background spans over 53 years of undergraduate, graduate, and post-graduate work. He holds 5 master’s and 4 doctorates. === Publications === * Penerapan image classification dengan pre-trained model mobilenet dalam client-side machine learning * Investigating critical success factors in agile systems development projects * Pengembangan Aplikasi E-office Pencatatan Dokumen Pada Badan Kepegawaian Daerah Provinsi Jawa Barat Dengan Menggunakan Metode Rad * A framework for deciding how to pick the right methodology * Application of QUEST model of questioning in the classroom: action research methodology in high school education * Multiple faces detection based on HSV colour space * Dynamic resource monitoring system with dynamic aggregate view * AnaEx: An Expert System Solution to Anaerobic Bacterial Identifications * Sistema di misura dei consumi di unita di calcolo low-power per applicazioni scientifiche presso il centro INFN-CNAF == Awards == * Nominated Member in Alfred Whitehead Leadership Society * Who's Who in California * Who’s Who in the West * Who’s Who in America America == References ==
title: Clifford Kettemborough
